Requirements befor installation
1-check MAC addrress and UUID for be not same Mac in nods 
ip link
cat /sys/class/dmi/id/product_uuid
2-disable swap
comment section swap in /etc/fstab
reboot
verify with free -m
3-Update and Upgrade
apt update
apt upgrade -y
4-Dns electro in /etc/resolve.conf -->78.157.42.100
for install kubernetes We Used Containerd so First we should install containerd
5-cd /usr/local/
6-wget https://github.com/containerd/containerd/releases/download/v1.6.30/containerd-1.6.30-linux-amd64.tar.gz
tar xzf containerd-1.6.30-linux-amd64.tar.gz
7-wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/containerd/containerd/main/containerd.service
8-mv containerd.service /usr/lib/systemd/system/
9-systemctl daemon-reload
10-systemctl enable --now containerd.service
install runc --> for namespace and cgroup
11-wget https://github.com/opencontainers/runc/releases/download/v1.1.12/runc.amd64
12-install -m 755 runc.amd64 /usr/local/sbin/runc
13-runc --version
14-containerd config default | sudo tee /etc/containerd/config.toml
15-sudo systemctl daemon-reload
16-systemctl restart containerd
17-wget https://github.com/containernetworking/plugins/releases/download/v1.4.0/cni-plugins-linux-amd64-v1.4.0.tgz
18-mkdir -p /opt/cni/bin
19-tar -xzvf cni-plugins-linux-amd64-v1.4.0.tgz -C /opt/cni/bin

